Title: A Package for a PCA Like Procedure Suited for Multivariate Extreme Value Distributions
Package: maxstablePCA
Type: Package
Description: Dimension reduction for multivariate data of extreme events with a PCA like procedure. Tools for necessary transformations of the data are provided. 
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Felix Reinbott <felix.reinbott@ovgu.de>
